<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 01:06:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加密货币公司 Zerohash 申请国家信托银行执照</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/crypto-firm-zerohash-applies-for-national-trust-bank-charter</link><description>数字资产公司 Zero Hash US LLC 向美国货币监理署提交了一份国家信托银行执照申请。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iuxwMq_Y8oPg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 20:51:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/crypto-firm-zerohash-applies-for-national-trust-bank-charter</guid></item><item><title>人工智能的繁荣刺激了比特币销售，对持有 80 亿美元的矿商构成了威胁</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/ai-boom-spurs-bitcoin-sales-threat-at-miners-holding-8-billion</link><description>多年来，最大的比特币矿商在经营时都遵循着一种信念和商业模式：他们铸造的比特币值得持有，稀缺性会奖励耐心，数字货币的资产负债表积累本身就是一种竞争护城河。他们中的一些人建立了价值数亿美元的藏品。他们称之为财政战略。公牛队称之为信念。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyYdy0sIE6xI/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 20:44:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/ai-boom-spurs-bitcoin-sales-threat-at-miners-holding-8-billion</guid></item><item><title>Kraken 是第一家确保美联储支付访问权限的加密货币公司</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/crypto-exchange-kraken-secures-fed-payment-access</link><description>Kraken 已获得堪萨斯城联邦储备银行授予的有限用途账户，使其成为第一家直接访问美国央行支付基础设施的数字资产银行。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i1.bNVXDduTE/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 12:48:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/crypto-exchange-kraken-secures-fed-payment-access</guid></item><item><title>Tradeweb 通过押注外汇风格市场推动加密货币发展</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/tradeweb-makes-crypto-push-with-bet-on-fx-style-market-structure</link><description>机构资金开始从加密货币交易所转移到看起来更像华尔街的场外交易场所。 Tradeweb Markets Inc. 领投了 3100 万美元，认为这种转变才刚刚开始。&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="http://assets.bwbx.io/images/iP8D8NG6dNzI/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/tradeweb-makes-crypto-push-with-bet-on-fx-style-market-structure</guid></item><item><title>伊朗 78 亿美元的加密货币市场在战争中引起新的关注</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/iran-s-7-8-billion-crypto-market-draws-fresh-attention-in-war</link><description>美国和以色列对伊朗的战争让该国 78 亿美元的加密货币市场重新受到关注，该国公民和当局在动荡时期越来越多地转向该市场存储和汇款。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ilsFYJFUvElw/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 13:00:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/iran-s-7-8-billion-crypto-market-draws-fresh-attention-in-war</guid></item><item><title>渣打银行任命前摩根大通高管 Mallela 领导支付业务</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/stanchart-appoints-former-jpmorgan-exec-mallela-to-lead-payments</link><description>渣打银行已任命摩根大通区块链部门前全球联席主管领导其全球支付业务，并继续对其现金管理系统进行现代化改造。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/im6YV5s8adrs/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/stanchart-appoints-former-jpmorgan-exec-mallela-to-lead-payments</guid></item><item><title>特朗普就加密议程与银行的对抗升级</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/trump-escalates-confrontation-with-banks-over-crypto-agenda</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普总统警告银行不要削弱他的加密货币议程，并推动通过一项名为《清晰法案》的市场结构法案，从而加剧了与金融业在重塑美国数字资产监管方式的立法问题上的对抗。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/irTCQOplopOg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 23:19:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/trump-escalates-confrontation-with-banks-over-crypto-agenda</guid></item><item><title>由于长期战争的风险给加密货币带来压力，比特币回落</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/bitcoin-btc-slide-starts-anew-as-iran-uncertainty-drags-on</link><description>由于人们越来越担心伊朗战争将继续升级，风险资产的更广泛抛售加剧，比特币徘徊在 68,000 美元左右，抹去了周一的涨幅。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioDoooC3HqMo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 08:10:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/bitcoin-btc-slide-starts-anew-as-iran-uncertainty-drags-on</guid></item><item><title>塞勒强调向企业推销时的安全性</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-03/strategy-s-saylor-puts-emphasis-on-safety-in-latest-sales-pitch-to-corporations</link><description>永久安全策略&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iDHgeMoK8x_0/v6/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 22:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-03/strategy-s-saylor-puts-emphasis-on-safety-in-latest-sales-pitch-to-corporations</guid></item><item><title>CFTC 主席表示，美国加密货币永续期货即将推出</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/us-crypto-linked-perpetual-futures-coming-soon-cftc-chair-says</link><description>美国最高衍生品监管机构计划在几周内允许加密货币的永续期货合约，将迄今为止几乎完全存在于离岸交易所的交易工具引入境内。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iOgtymQCiZNE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 19:07:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/us-crypto-linked-perpetual-futures-coming-soon-cftc-chair-says</guid></item><item><title>欧洲央行文件警告称，稳定币可能对货币政策构成重大风险</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/stablecoins-could-pose-major-risks-to-monetary-policy-ecb-paper</link><description>欧洲央行的一份工作文件警告称，稳定币的广泛采用将对欧元区银行和欧洲央行的货币主权构成重大风险，特别是与美元等外币挂钩时。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyn1khea7JJk/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/stablecoins-could-pose-major-risks-to-monetary-policy-ecb-paper</guid></item><item><title>红杉资本和创始人为 Latam 的 ARQ 筹集 7000 万美元资金</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/sequoia-founders-fund-back-70-million-raise-for-latam-s-arq</link><description>ARQ 表示，风险投资公司红杉资本和 Founders Fund 正在通过融资 7000 万美元投资拉丁美洲金融应用程序 ARQ。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iiNyS2Imx3rw/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/sequoia-founders-fund-back-70-million-raise-for-latam-s-arq</guid></item></channel></rss>